text:
Posted an hour ago 0 
The lovable Stevie T presented an interesting little video today, featuring classic gentle acoustic songs combined with Cannibal Corpse lyrics. 
You can check it all out below. 
1) Eric Clapton - Tears in heaven + Butchered at Birth 2) Green Day - Good Ridance (Time of Your Life) + Force Fed Broken Glass 3) Plain White Ts - Hey There Delilah + Rancid Amputation 4) Extreme - More Than Words + Mangled 5) Guns N' Roses - Patience + Worm Infested 6) The Who - Behind Blue Eyes + Rabid 7) Metallica - Nothing Else Matters + Edible Autopsy 8) Eagles - Love Will Keep Us Alive + Mangled
